oxa'' | | Jianshangou Bed | | A [[Phasmatodea|stick insect]] |- |rowspan=5| ''[[Ilerdocossus]]'' | ''I. beipiaoensis'' | | | |rowspan=5| [[Cicada]]s<ref name=menonetal2005>{{cite journal | last1 = Menon | first1 = F. | last2 = Heads | first2 = S.W. | last3 = Martill | first3 = D.M. | year = 2005 | title = New Palaeontinidae (Insecta: Cicadomorpha) from the Lower Cretaceous Crato Formation of Brazil | url = | journal = Cretaceous Research | volume = 26 | issue = 6| pages = 837–844 | doi = 10.1016/j.cretres.2005.05.005 }}</ref> |- | ''I. exiguus'' | | | |- | ''I. fengningensis'' | | | |- | ''I. hui'' | | | |- | ''I. pingquanensis'' | | | |- | ''[[Kalligramma]]'' | ''K. liaoningensis'' | | Jianshangou Bed | | A [[Neuroptera|lacewing]] |- | ''[[Karatavoblatta]]'' | ''K. formosa'' | | | | A [[cockroach]]<ref name=lin&huang2001/> |- | ''[[Liaoaphidia]]'' | ''L. fornicata'' | | | | A snakefly<ref name=lin&huang2001/> |- | ''[[Liaonemobius]]'' | ''L. tanae'' | | | | A [[sword-tail cricket]]<ref name=ren2002/> |- | ''[[Longicellochrysa]]'' | ''L. yixiana'' | | | | A [[Mesochrysopidae|mesochrysopid]] lacewing<ref name=renmakarkin2010>{{cite journal | last1 = Ren | first1 = D. | last2 = Makarkin | first2 = V.N. | last3 = Yang | first3 = Q. | year = 2010 | title = A new fossil genus of Mesochrysopidae (Neuroptera) from the Early Cretaceous Yixian Formation of China | url = | journal = Zootaxa | volume = 2523 | issue = | pages = 50–56 }}</ref> |- | ''[[Mesascalaphus]]'' | ''M. yangi'' | | | | An [[owlfly]]<ref name=ren2002/> |- | ''[[Mesolygaeus]]'' | ''M. laiyangensis'' | | | | A water [[Hemiptera|bug]]<ref name=lin&huang2001/> |- | ''[[Metabittacus]]'' | ''M. colosseus'' | | Jianshangou Bed | | |- | ''[[Miracossus]]'' | ''M. ingentius'' | | | | A cicada<ref name=menonetal2005/> |- | ''[[Nipponoblatta]]'' | ''N. acerba'' | | Jianshangou Bed | | A cockroach |- | ''[[Oloberotha]]'' | ''O. sinica'' | | | | A [[Berothidae|beaded lacewing]]<ref name=ren2002/> |- | ''[[Sinochresmoda]